      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines. they dont help. they just tell me to breathe or something. it doesnt change the fact that i have 3 finals next week and i'm already failing everything. it just feels like a massive loop of failure that never stops. like, what is even the point of pushing through all this just to stay stuck in the same hole?",
